Package: poco
Type: Package
Title: poco (POsterior COmpression): Compress Bayesian Posteriors Using Mixture and Density Approximations
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Chen", "Zhan", , "chen.zhan@adelaide.edu.au",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Stefano", "Mangiola", , "mangiola.s@wehi.edu.au",
           role = "aut"))
Description: Provides a unified interface for compressing Markov chain Monte
    Carlo (MCMC) posterior draws into compact density approximations
    (Gaussian mixture models or kernel density estimates), and for
    regenerating samples and evaluating density on demand. Supports raw
    posterior matrices and 'cmdstanr', 'brms', and 'sccomp' fits, with
    pluggable methods selected via a single `method` argument.
